0.2.4.name: wordpress/pricing-table-ready
0.2.4.description:
With WordPress Pricing Table plugin you can manage pricing table, publish pricing table on WordPress page or post. Pricing Table Ready! plugin include five different styles so you can choose style for your online store or blog. Create Responsive pricing table, comparison table is also available to creation.

To insert pricing table use shortocode:

  • [ready-pricing-tables id=123 template=tiny]
  • id price template ID
  • template template design name

Features:

  • Five different table templates
  • Pricing Table live preview
  • Easy to use price table generator
  • Drag and drop columns
  • Unlimited columns and rows
  • Button, text, special style for any pricing gird
